    <entry>
      <title>I’m Nobody! Who are you?——Emily Dickinson</title>
      <link href="2020/12/08/imnobody/"/>
      <url>2020/12/08/imnobody/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>I’m Nobody! Who are you? </p><p><em>我谁都不是！你是？</em></p><p>Emily Dickinson</p><p><em>艾米莉·狄金森</em></p><p>I’m Nobody! Who are you?</p><p><em>我谁都不是！你是？</em></p><p>Are you – Nobody – too?</p><p><em>你 是否 也是？</em></p><p>Then there’s a pair of us!</p><p><em>那我们正合适！</em></p><p>Don’t tell! they’d advertise – you know!</p><p><em>嘘！如你所知，他们会广而告之！</em></p><p>How dreary – to be – Somebody!</p><p><em>为博出名，世风日下！</em></p><p>How public – like a Frog –</p><p><em>庸如青蛙 ！</em></p><p>To tell one’s name – the livelong June –</p><p><em>终日呱呱，自说自话</em>。</p><p>To an admiring Bog!</p><p><em>似陷泥沼，愈捧愈杀！</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
